═══ UNIQUE SCOPE OF THIS CHAPTER ═══
This chapter OWNS loss modeling and stressed cash flows.
DO NOT re-identify or rank risks (covered in ch11), re-describe covenants (ch10),
or repeat return decomposition math (ch08). Every paragraph must quantify a downside
outcome — stressed IRR, loss given default, recovery mechanics, or time-to-exit.
Qualitative risk narrative belongs in ch11. This chapter is the numbers under stress.

